data.description: Beautiful modern Farmette located near the heart of Westminster! Bring your horses, goats, and chickens or adopt some of the residents! Some features include a barn with two matted stalls, large overhang and separate hay/tack room.  Three board fence with no climb wire divided into three separate areas  with new electric and water ran out to the field-pasture for the horses, dry lot with barn, and smaller wooded pasture with mini barn for goats, pigs...anything you can imagine. And these are all less than 2 years old! Chicken lovers dream-brand new twenty-four foot chicken shed with four separate runs and its own electric!  Beautiful views of the horses and countryside adorn the dining room, kitchen, and two bedrooms.  Truly an animal lovers oasis!   A property like THIS with a young and spacious colonial home boasting of modern touches throughout,  hardwood floors, updated systems, views, and an incredible layout is a RARE find!  This home sits on 3.6 gorgeous acres of flat land backing up to a serene corn field. You will feel the peacefulness of natures seclusions but still able to enjoy the community of a small neighborhood. The traditional layout offers all of the spaces you will need to entertain and relax, as well as being  pleasantly surprised by the open concept of the large kitchen with eat-in dining area leading into the family room. This sunshine filled room has vaulted ceilings and a cozy wood stove while the sliding glass doors open to huge back deck partially covered and perfect to enjoy every season.  Main level living is easily obtained with this layout - offering the laundry room, a spacious bedroom & a full bathroom. This is the perfect opportunity for a first floor owners suite or in-law suite. There is also ramp entry available through the garage & first floor doors are also wheelchair accessible. Upstairs you will find 4 sizeable bedrooms and an additional den perfect for a private office! Three out of 4 of these bedrooms have walk in closets, and the 4th has a double closet- dreamy right? Moving along to the walk out basement with 10 foot ceilings. With this open concept, incredibly large, blank slate you can use your imagination and create a 6th bedroom, a gym, a play area for kids, home theatre, bar, additional family room, leave it as storage, make it a separate apartment or do ALL of the above....the possibilities are truly endless.  Inquire for more details or videos of the land/current use. This homestead is move in ready for you and your personal touches! Set up a private tour of this gem
